        "contentSchemaVersion": "3.0.0",
        "displayName": "ContosoFort",
        "publisherDisplayName": "ContosoFort",
        "descriptionHtml": "<p><strong>Note:</strong> Please refer to the following before installing the solution:</p>\n<p>• Review the solution <a href=\"https://github.com/Azure/Azure-Sentinel/tree/master/Solutions/ContosoFort/ReleaseNotes.md\">Release Notes</a></p>\n<p>• There may be <a href=\"https://aka.ms/sentinelsolutionsknownissues\">known issues</a> pertaining to this Solution, please refer to them before installing.</p>\n<p>The ContosoFort solution provides the capability to ingest ContosoFort security event logs into Microsoft Sentinel using ContosoFort Log Export and Azure Blob Storage via the Codeless Connector Framework (CCF).</p>\n<p><strong>Underlying Microsoft Technologies used:</strong></p>\n<p>This solution takes a dependency on the following technologies:</p>\n<ol type=\"a\">\n<li><p><a href=\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/sentinel/create-codeless-connector\">Codeless Connector Framework</a></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><a href=\"https://azure.microsoft.com/services/storage/blobs/\">Azure Blob Storage</a></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><a href=\"https://azure.microsoft.com/services/event-grid/\">Azure Event Grid</a></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Data Connectors:</strong> 1</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://aka.ms/azuresentinel\">Learn more about Microsoft Sentinel</a> | <a href=\"https://aka.ms/azuresentinelsolutionsdoc\">Learn more about Solutions</a></p>\n",
